{"tid":187303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"匯豐加大力度打擊洗黑錢活動　要求客戶更新資料","createTime":"2017-04-05T00:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T01:21:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caf357e347299020dcad48fc77fddc537c4bf4a1","tid":187303,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/20160504160643141_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2F20160504160643141_m.jpg&h=45f98aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前再次捲入協助俄羅斯洗黑錢之調查，為進一步打擊有關活動，香港匯豐去年起去信客戶要求其更新資料，匯豐香港區行政總裁施穎茵表示，今年將加大有關規模，要求零售銀行客戶提供住址、聯繫方式、職業、收入及賬戶用途等資料及文件，工商金融客戶則提供其公司之業務性質、擁有權架構、業務營運所在國家、資金來源及賬戶用途等證明文件。若客戶未能於規定之30-60日內提供有關資料及文件，銀行或會凍結其帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，部份客戶或須提交額外資料，若發現可疑個案，亦會上報政府之聯合財富情報組。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.795296/popular-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-content%2FNOW.795296%2Fpopular-news&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a7277c84\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.795296/popular-news</a>"},{"pid":"0dc6d824465f031b0c5f66af68c36f84eb212e4b","tid":187303,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:03:21.000Z","msg":"更佢老母，垃圾銀行，直接取消"},{"pid":"d18afb4a5003903c54dab9cac8e2887126445476","tid":187303,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"又黎跑數sell保險"},{"pid":"274ccd5c8138ceae88791f732656c829c7a2cb9d","tid":187303,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又黎跑數sell保險</blockquote><br />\n呢句真呀<br />\n<br />\n銀行職員會搵你: 話冇人係你經理 你買我D保險等我做你經理幫你拆掂佢啦<br />\n好啦 你買左保險<br />\n<br />\n一年之後<br />\n先生: 你好呀 我地係X瘋銀行既職員呀 麻煩你為戶口提供少少資料<br />\n呀, o個位經理冇o係我地公司做喇 你有冇儲錢呀 不如我幫你儲錢順便做埋你經理幫你處理更新資料呀<br />\n<br />\nendless loop"},{"pid":"4aaed7963138c8cbc3af784e4545a1573f0760bc","tid":187303,"uid":7169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"加你老母力度"},{"pid":"66208c2c6dba407a1b85ae5a10be50b5cf9c5bfa","tid":187303,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}